## Whatâ€˜s the problem?

`reqwest::redirect::Policy::limited`  redirects is 1 less than the maxmium, thats say If the maxmium limit set 1, than it won't redirect.

IMO, It doesn't quite conform to the description in the document

> Create a Policy with a maximum number of redirects. An Error will be returned if the max is reached.



